Class CountingSet<T>

java.lang.Object

Type Parameters:

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.Set<T>
@ThreadSafe
public final class CountingSet<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.Set<T>

A thread-safe Set that keeps track of how many times an element has been added. The set can be dumped as a list in asc or desc order of how many times an element was added.
